      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Grant Osborne</b>\n</p><p><b>Grant Osborne</b>,<br />\na British computer chess programmer, and author of the chess program <a href=\"/AtlanChess\" title=\"AtlanChess\">AtlanChess</a>. \nGrant Osborne was involved in finding dense <a href=\"/Best_Magics_so_far\" title=\"Best Magics so far\">Magics</a> for <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, \nand proposed <a href=\"/Kindergarten_Bitboards#MagicCompression\" title=\"Kindergarten Bitboards\">Magic Compression</a> for <a href=\"/Kindergarten_Bitboards\" title=\"Kindergarten Bitboards\">Kindergarten Bitboards</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grant_Osborne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?t=5997\">A Faster Magic Move Bitboard Generator?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Grant Osborne</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, December 15, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=196157&amp;t=21329\">Incorporating the shift into the magic number</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Grant Osborne</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22550\">Bitboard of Pinned Pieces</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Grant Osborne</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2008</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grant_Osborne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?t=5997\">A Faster Magic Move Bitboard Generator?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Grant Osborne</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, December 15, 2006</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=198660&amp;t=21329\">Re: How to reduce the \"bits\" used in a magic number</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Grant Osborne</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 04, 2008</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228173127\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.006 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 39/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 94/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report